#: ''the cheese '''hoop''', or cylinder in which the curd is pressed in making cheese''
# {{context|mostly|in plural|lang=en}} A circle, or combination of circles, of thin [[whalebone]], metal, or other elastic material, used for expanding the skirts of ladies' dresses; [[crinoline]].
